title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Natural areas, Northern Sweden, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Natural areas, Northern Sweden, 2008
description: This dataset shows natural areas in Northern Sweden. Natural Areas consist of water, riverbanks, parks, forests, and other feature types. Because the dataset for the entire country was too big, it was divided into northern, southeastern and southwestern Sweden.Together, the datasets have more almost 12,000 features for various natural areas.
